descriptionHTML:
SillyWatchFace is an watch face for Android Wear. Looking at the time is a boring thing to do every day. Let's make it fun with these silly names given to hours and minutes.

NOTE: This works on only watches Moto 360, Asus Zenwatch, LG G Watch R, Sony Smartwatch 3 etc.
This does NOT work on non Android Wear watches like Pebble, Samsung Gear, Smartwatch 2 etc.

1 = bun
2 = too
3 = tree
4 = foe
. . . and so on,
and then . . .
11 = leven
12 = twill
13 = tuttin
. . .and so on,
similarly . .
20 = venti
30 = tatti
40 = potty
. . . and so on
